type":"text","text":"圈来自oblique (adj.斜的，歪的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"irredeemable","headword":"irredeemable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.无法挽回的，不可救药的(incapable of being remedied)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'di:mabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ir（不）+redeem（挽回，弥补）+able→无法挽回的，不可救药的"},{"type":"entry","text":"untreated","headword":"untreated"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 未治疗的(not receiving medical treatment);未经处理的(in a natural state)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'tri:tid]"},{"type":"entry","text":"egoist","headword":"egoist"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.自我主义者(a believer in egoism)"},{"type":"text","text":"chart"},{"type":"text","text":"['i:gaurst]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自ego（n.自我）"},{"type":"entry","text":"drizzly","headword":"drizzly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj毛毛细雨的"},{"type":"text","text":"[drizli]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆注意该单词虽以-ly结尾，但不是副词，而是形容词"}]},{"number":387,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"outspoken","headword":"outspoken"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 坦率的，直言不讳的(direct and open in speech or expression)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aut'spaukan]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：out（出）+spoken（口头的，说的）→说出来的→直言不讳的"},{"type":"text","text":"While Parker is very outspoken on issues she cares about, she is not"},{"type":"text","text":"fanatical; she concedes the strength of opposing arguments when they expose"},{"type":"text","text":"weaknesses inherent in her own."},{"type":"entry","text":"glossary","headword":"glossary"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 词汇表(a list of difficult, technical, or foreign terms with definitions or"},{"type":"text","text":"['gla:sari]"},{"type":"text","text":"translations)"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：gloss（舌头；语言）+ary→词汇表"},{"type":"entry","text":"regale","headword":"regale"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.款待，宴请（to feast with delicacies);使-快乐(to give pleasure)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'gerl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：re（使）+gale（高兴）→使客人高兴→款待"},{"type":"entry","text":