:"园联想记忆：f+ray（光线）→时光催人老→磨破"},{"type":"entry","text":"pestilential","headword":"pestilential"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.引起癌疫的（causing or tending to cause pestilence），致命的；极"},{"type":"text","text":"[pestr'len]"},{"type":"text","text":"讨厌的"},{"type":"text","text":"deadly, irritating"},{"type":"entry","text":"unsuspecting","headword":"unsuspecting"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不怀疑的，无猜疑的，可信任的(feeling no suspicion,trusting)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Ansa'spektrn]"},{"type":"entry","text":"indestructible","headword":"indestructible"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不能破坏的，不可毁灭的(incapable of being destroyed，ruined, or rendered"},{"type":"text","text":"[rndr'straktabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"ineffective)"},{"type":"entry","text":"inflict","headword":"inflict"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使遭受（痛苦、损伤等)(to cause sth.unpleasant to be endured)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xn'flrkt]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（使）+flict(打击）→使受打击→使遭受（痛苦、损伤等）"},{"type":"entry","text":"physiological","headword":"physiological"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.生理（技能）的（of，or concerning the bodily functions);生理学的（of，or"},{"type":"text","text":"[fizia'la:dzrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"concerning physiology)"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自physiology（n.生理学）"},{"type":"entry","text":"contemplative","headword":"contemplative"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 沉思的(marked by or given to contemplation) n. 沉思者(a person who"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'templatrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"practices contemplation)"},{"type":"entry","text":"threadlike","headword":"threadlike"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad线状的"},{"type":"text","text":"['eredlark]"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：thread（线）+like（像-一样）→像线一样→线状的"},{"type":"entry","text":"discourteous","headword":"discourteous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.失礼的，粗鲁的（lacking courtesy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dis'ks:rtias]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：dis（离开）+court（宫廷）+eous→远离宫廷的→村野匹夫的→失礼的，"},{"type":"text","text":"粗鲁的"}]},{"number":390,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 35 >>>"},{"type":"text","text":"It is possible to analyze a literary work to death, dlissecting what should be a"},{"type":"text","text":"living experience as if it were a laboratory specimen."},{"type":"entry","text":"vanity","headword":"vanity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 虚荣, 自负(inflated pride in oneself; conceit)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vaenati]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：van（空）+ity→空虚→虚荣"},{"type":"text","text":"It is ironic that a critic of such overwhelming vanity now suffers from a"},{"type":"text","text":"measure of the oblivion to which he was forever consigning others; in the end, all"},{"type":"text","text":"his self-adulation has only worked against him."},{"type":"entry","text":"impracticability","headword":"impracticability"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.无法实施；不能实施的事项"},{"type":"text","text":"[m,praektrkabilati]"},{"type":"text","text":"The impracticability of such utopian notions is reflected by the quick"},{"type":"text","text":"disintegration of the idealistic community at Brooke Farm."},{"type":"entry","text":"schematic","headword":"schematic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 纲要的, 图解的(of, relating to, or in the form of a scheme or diagram)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ski:'maetrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自schema（n.图表；纲要）"},{"type":"entry","text":"defunct","headword":"defunct"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj死亡的（dead or extinct)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'fankt]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：de（否定）+funct活动）→不活动的→死亡的"},{"type":"entry","text":"fruitlessly","headword":"fruitlessly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adv.徒劳地，无益地（unproductively)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fru:tlasli]"},{"type":"entry","text":"unprofitably","headword":"unprofitably"},{"type":"entry","text":"undeserving","headword":"undeserving"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不值得的(not deserving to have or receive sth.)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andr'z3:rvin]"},{"type":"entry","text":"unworthy","headword":"unworthy"},{"type":"entry","text":"imposture","headword":"imposture"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 冒充(being an impostor; fraud)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rm'pa:st[ar]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：im（进入）+pos（放）+ture→把别的东西放进去→冒充"},{"type":"entry","text":"denote","headword":"denote"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.指示，表示（to mark,indicate; signify)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（加强）+not（知道）+e→让人知道→表示"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'naut]"},{"type":"entry","text":"unrestricted","headword":"unrestricted"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 无限制的，自由的(not limited by anyone or anything)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Anrt'strrktrd]"},{"type":"entry","text":"rueful","headword":"rueful"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj抱撼的(feeling or showing pity or sympathy)：后悔的，侮恨的(mournful,"},{"type":"text","text":"['ru:fl]"},{"type":"text","text":"regretful)"},{"type":"entry","text":"unskilled","headword":"unskilled"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不熟练的(lacking skill or technical training);无需技能的(not requiring skill)"}]},{"number":391,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"frenetic","headword":"frenetic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.狂乱的，发狂的(frantic,frenzied)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fra'netik]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：fren（看作phren，心灵）+etic→心灵承受不了的→狂乱的，发狂的"},{"type":"entry","text":"rip","headword":"rip"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 撕， 撕裂(to tear or split apart or open)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rxp]"},{"type":"text","text":"rip at sth.猛烈撕扯;用力割"},{"type":"entry","text":"semimolten","headword":"semimolten"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad半熔化的"},{"type":"text","text":"[semi'maultan]"},{"type":"entry","text":"afflict","headword":"afflict"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 折磨;使痛苦(to cause persistent pain or suffering)"},{"type":"text","text":"[afrkt]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：af（去）+flict（打击）一一再打击→折磨：使痛苦"},{"type":"entry","text":"escapism","headword":"escapism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 逃避现实(的习气)(the tendency to escape from daily realities by means of"},{"type":"text","text":"[t'skexpizam]"},{"type":"text","text":"entertainment)"},{"type":"entry","text":"underutilized","headword":"underutilized"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj未充分利用的"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andar'ju:talarzd]"},{"type":"text","text":"过词根记忆：under（不足）+utilize（利用）+d→未充分利用的"},{"type":"entry","text":"amiability","headword":"amiability"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.亲切，友善(the state of being friendly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ermia'brlati]"},{"type":"text","text":"agreeableness, cordiality, geniality, pleasance, pleasantness"},{"type":"entry","text":"extricable","headword":"extricable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 可解数的，能脱险的(capable of being freed from dlifficulty)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ekstrikabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ex（外面）+tric（小障碍物）+able→能据脱小障碍物的→可解救的"},{"type":"entry","text":"assuredness","headword":"assuredness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.确定：自信"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'furdnas]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自assure（v.使确信）"},{"type":"entry","text":"abatement","headword":"abatement"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.减少,减轻(the act or process of abating)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'bertmant]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自abate（v.减轻，减弱）"},{"type":"entry","text":"amaze","headword":"amaze"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使大为吃惊，使惊奇（tofill with wonder)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'meiz]"},{"type":"text","text":"astound, dumbfound, flabbergast"},{"type":"entry","text":"blockbuster","headword":"blockbuster"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.巨型炸弹(a very large high-explosive bomb);—鸣惊人的事物：非常成功的书"},{"type":"text","text":"['bla:kbAstar]"},{"type":"text","text":"或电影"},{"type":"entry","text":"encapsulation","headword":"encapsulation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.包装(packing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn,kaepsju'ler[n]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自encapsulate（v封装）"},{"type":"entry","text":"deprecation","headword":"deprecation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 反对(disapproval)"},{"type":"text","text":"[depra'ker{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自deprecate（v反对）"},{"type":"entry","text":"tidy","headword":"tidy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj整齐的，整洁的（neat and orderly)：相当好的"},{"type":"text","text":"['tardi]"},{"type":"text","text":"shipshape, trim, uncluttered"},{"type":"entry","text":"culminate","headword":"culminate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 达到顶点(to rise to or form a summit);使达到最高点(to bring to a head or to"},{"type":"text","text":"[kAlminert]"},{"type":"text","text":"the highest point)"},{"type":"entry","text":"rectify","headword":"rectify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 改正, 矫正(to correct by removing errors; adjust); 提纯(to purify by repeated"},{"type":"text","text":"['rektrfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"distillation)"},{"type":"text","text":"围词根记忆：rect（直）+ify→使··变直→改正，矫正"}]},{"number":392,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 35 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"unnoteworthy","headword":"unnoteworthy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj不显著的，不值得注意的"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'nautws:rdi]"},{"type":"entry","text":"insecure","headword":"insecure"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj无保障的，不安全的(not adequately guarded or sustained)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,nsr'kjur]"},{"type":"text","text":"unprotected, unsafe"},{"type":"entry","text":"equate","headword":"equate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.认为相等或相仿(to consider sth. as equal to sth.else)"},{"type":"text","text":"[i'kwert]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：equ（相等的）+ate（表动作）→使相等→认为相等或相仿"},{"type":"entry","text":"interactive","headword":"interactive"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.交互式的(mutually or reciprocally active)"},{"type":"text","text":"[intar'aektiv]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自interact（v相互作用，相互影响）"},{"type":"entry","text":"cannily","headword":"cannily"},{"type":"definition","text":"adv.机灵地"},{"type":"text","text":"['kaenrli]"},{"type":"entry","text":"outlast","headword":"outlast"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.比-持久"},{"type":"text","text":"[aut'laest]"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：out（超越）+last(坚持）→比-持久"},{"type":"entry","text":"preconception","headword":"preconception"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.先入之见(a preconceived idea);偏见(prejudice)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pri:kan'sepfn]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈联想记忆：pre（预先）+conception（观念）→先入之见"},{"type":"entry","text":"destine","headword":"destine"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.命运注定，预定（to decree beforehand)"},{"type":"text","text":"['destin]"},{"type":"text","text":"foreordain, predestine"},{"type":"entry","text":"carnage","headword":"carnage"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.大屠杀，残杀(bloody and extensive slaughter)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:rnid3]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：cam（肉）+age→（把人）切成肉的行为→大屠杀"},{"type":"text","text":"bloodbath, massacre"},{"type":"entry","text":"spanking","headword":"spanking"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.强烈的（strong)：疾行的(fast)"},{"type":"text","text":"['spaenkin]"},{"type":"text","text":"at a spanking pace/rate 步伐/速度非常快地"},{"type":"entry","text":"stellar","headword":"stellar"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 星的，星球的(of or relating to the stars)"},{"type":"text","text":"['stelar]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：stell(星星）+ar→星的，星球的"},{"type":"text","text":"留 Although supernovas are among the most luminous of cosmic events, these"},{"type":"text","text":"stellar explosions are often hard to detect, either because they are enormously"},{"type":"text","text":"far away or because they are dimmed by intervening dust and gas clouds."},{"type":"entry","text":"devour","headword":"devour"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.狼吞虎咽地吃，吞食（to eat or eat up hungrily)）：贪婪地看（或听、读等)(to enjoy"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'vauar]"},{"type":"text","text":"avidly)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：de（向下）+vour（看作vor，吃）→吞食"},{"type":"entry","text":"flock","headword":"flock"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 羊群; 乌群(a group of certain animals, as goats or sheep, or of birds)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fla:k]"},{"type":"text","text":"crowd, drove, horde, host, legion, mass"},{"type":"entry","text":"bleach","headword":"bleach"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.去色，漂白（to cause sth.to become white)n.漂白剂：漂